# Server-only Local test override: local, preview, or production.
# Leave empty for normal development. On Vercel, VERCEL_ENV is authoritative;
# a conflicting YOUTOOLA_ENV fails explicitly and can never elevate Preview.
# Never put secrets under NEXT_PUBLIC_*. Future variables must document whether
# they are Local, Preview or Production scoped and whether they are build-time
# or runtime configuration.
YOUTOOLA_ENV=
